title: My Dolphin Show v2.1.17 mod & data
description:
Take control of a cute dolphin and do the show in this great Adventure !  

IMPRESS THE AUDIENCE BY DOING TRICKS
Welcome to the paradise of aquatic animals. The trainer and her dolphin are ready to impress the audience with a specular show by doing all sorts of mini games. This is not a small aquarium, but big show like you would see in Sea World or any other water park. 
Jump into the swimming pool and do amazing tricks with your dolphin:
Beach ball hit, donut jumping, hurdle jumping, splash the audience wet, jump through rings, score a soccer goal, coin collect, piÃ±ata smash, air stunts, water walk, bowling, basketball, love kiss, golf, volleyball, collect fish from the trainer, underwater ring, fetch the ball game, hit the bell and many more fun tricks.

MAKE YOUR DOLPHIN EVEN MORE CUTE
Dolphins are also fashionista ! Make your pet stylish with 47 fun outfits :
Cheerleader, ghost, pink dolphin, clown fish, banana, lobster, zebra, crocodile, princess, shark, tiger, turtle, scuba diving suit, wedding dress, fairy, polar bear, wolf, sea lion, celebrity, angel, baby whale, Hawaii dress, Dracula, silver dolphin, mermaid, Santa, frog, super dolphin, penguin, hippo, gold dolphin, seahorse, rainbow dolphin, glitter dolphin and more.

PERFORM YOUR SHOW ALL AROUND THE WORLD
The game has 126 levels and more are coming. Youâ€™ll be putting on shows in these locations:
Hawaii Lagoon and his crystal-clear water, Cruise ship (love boat), Las Vegas Park, Amazing theme park, water amusement park, Jungle.
Go for Olympic gold and swim through the coral and win those 3 golden stars in each show!

FEATURES OF MY DOLPHIN SHOW 
* Free Game !
* Unique simulation of dolphin
* Console Quality 3D Graphics
* 47 Fun outfits/animals/pets to unlock
* 126 challenges filled with cool mini games
* 6 Aquatic Parks & Zoo available
* Intuitive Gameplay & controllers
* Collect coins and Customize your dolphin
